# Lamp Room — Illustration Prompt

Create a richly detailed, roughly square digital painting sized to sit beside narrative text on desktop or mobile screens. Depict a grounded late-medieval harbor campaign setting with oily lantern hardware, shutters, sliding plates, hooks, shelves, and soot-dark timbers. Emphasize crisp readability, brighter maritime color accents, and clear spatial separation more than muddy painterly atmosphere.

- Composition: cramped interior of the lamp room with a visible doorway back out to the tower stair.
- Key elements: lantern slides, oil pots, wall racks, soot, and signal apparatus in ordered confusion.
- Character focus: tower keepers confident that a wrong lantern component is not a real delay.
- Navigation hint: make the exit back to the tower immediately readable.

